  r = BuildPipelineResult(False, '', True, '', False, '', True, '', False); \
  print('Failed:', r.get_failure_summary())"
# Output: Failed: mojo-build, mojo-test

# Syntax check
python -m py_compile src/scylla/e2e/llm_judge.py
# Output: ✓ Syntax check passed
```

### Integration Testing

